No. 11-7186. Clarence Hicks, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1088, 132 S. Ct. 833,

181 L. Ed. 2d 542,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8688, December 5, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
